## IDebugProtectedView interface

Factory for creating proxy objects that can be invalidated later. Once invalidated any property read that wasn't explicity marked safe will cause a debug error. Available in debug contexts only.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
export interface IDebugProtectedView<_T extends object>
```

## Methods

|  Method | Description |
|  --- | --- |
|  [createProtectedView(view)](./rc-js-util.idebugprotectedview.createprotectedview.md) | Create a proxy to the view, if invalidate called then access of non <code>safeKeys</code> will cause a debug error. |
|  [invalidate()](./rc-js-util.idebugprotectedview.invalidate.md) | Invalidates all previous views. |
